  "body": "<center><p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/VCOgABU.png\" /></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-api\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/Ol1Tcf8.png\" width=\"143\" height=\"50\" /></a> <a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/fabric-language-kotlin\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/c1DH9VL.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"171\" height=\"50\" /></a></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>ElytraBoosters</strong> is a mod by NotJustAnna which adds Elytra Boosters which aim to replace Minecraft's Firework Rockets.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">The boosters are craftable and come on multiple flavors: <strong>Standard</strong>&nbsp;Boosters (replaces the Firework Rocket), <strong>Short-burst</strong> Boosters (faster, doesn't last long) and <strong>Long-range</strong> Boosters (slower, but lasts the longest).</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\">There is also a <strong>Forward Launcher</strong>, which launches people with elytra (or alternatives) flying into the air.</p>\n<h4 style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong>Recipes:</strong></h4>\n<div class=\"spoiler\">\n<p><img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/qIgFXc6.png\" /></p>\n</div>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;</strong></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\">Join our Discord, that's the place for discuss stuff as well as the source of all sneak peeks of this mod!</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a title=\"Join Cafeteria Developtent!\" href=\"https://discord.gg/G4PjhEf\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://discord.com/api/guilds/707435077679841350/embed.png?style=banner2\" alt=\"\" width=\"320\" height=\"76\" /></a></p><center>",
